== Nickname == Screw it. You can't reach some people. [[User:Uncle Bubba|Uncle Bubba]] ([[User talk:Uncle Bubba|talk]]) 21:47, 15 April 2013 (UTC) :I've switched it back to the spelling used by his biographer in his book ({{cite book | last = Christman | first = Albert B. | title = Target Hiroshima: Deak Parsons and the Creation of the Atomic Bomb | location = Annapolis, Maryland | publisher = Naval Institute Press | year = 1998 | isbn = 1-55750-120-3 | oclc = 38257982 }}). This follows the form that Parsons used. As far as I can tell, Parsons always spelled it "Deak". (See Christman, pp. 32, 260-251) [[User:Hawkeye7|Hawkeye7]] ([[User talk:Hawkeye7|talk]]) 19:43, 15 April 2013 (UTC)
